      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>rice</strong> and 350ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> water to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat, once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</p>",
